# AWS Cost Report for Small Web Application

## Overview

This report provides a cost estimate for hosting a small web application on Amazon Web Services (AWS). The application requirements are:

* 2 vCPUs
* 4 GB RAM
* 100 GB storage
* 50 GB monthly outbound data transfer
* 24/7 availability (730 hours/month)

The estimate uses AWS On-Demand pricing and standard storage services.

